{"tid":553624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發20180207】花蓮餘震規模5.7最大震度4級 幾乎全台有感","createTime":"2018-02-07T15:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T19:01:56.000Z","uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6f088219977fcee6c5c2edee55867f1783fd31","tid":553624,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"花蓮餘震規模5.7最大震度4級 幾乎全台有感<br />\n發稿時間：2018/02/07 23:31最新更新：2018/02/07 23:43<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img5.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/800/20180207/53670356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg5.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F800%2F20180207%2F53670356.jpg&h=1630fa51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者陳葦庭台北7日電）花蓮昨天發生芮氏規模6.0地震，今天晚間再度發生芮氏規模5.7餘震，最大震度花蓮4級，台北震度2級，幾乎全台有感。<br />\n<br />\n6日晚間11時50分再度發生芮氏規模6.0地震，後續餘震已經超過180個，今天晚間11時21分又發生顯著有感餘震，芮氏規模5.7，地震深度10公里，花蓮、宜蘭、南投4級，雲林3級，台中、桃園、新竹、台東、台北、嘉義、彰化、苗栗2級，台南、高雄、屏東、澎湖1級。（編輯：陳清芳）1070207<br />\n<br />\n轉自中央通訊社<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201802075010-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201802075010-1.aspx&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=4ff51ddb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201802075010-1.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"3ac5441c238107100401eca4b259302353441eef","tid":553624,"uid":5787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩又黎?"},{"pid":"b8bc988455dff8ef02e07d6be6494caae0d381e9","tid":553624,"uid":35221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ac5441c238107100401eca4b259302353441eef","tid":553624,"uid":5787,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"岩岩又黎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"c7105b11ece342d631174f5fbb8a311930f312a0","tid":553624,"uid":20658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"傻撚左"},{"pid":"dc0dc603c3983b1a0da14bf4168886b35060186e","tid":553624,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53df72f9559d31277d267c5322bd666c063ba835","tid":553624,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://storm.mg/article/396664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstorm.mg%2Farticle%2F396664&d=%2BJcdb9KI6Gg6TMKANRyj05ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3c375adc\" target=\"_blank\">http://storm.mg/article/396664</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花蓮6日深夜地震引發4棟建築倒塌，7日晚間23點21分，花蓮再發生有感地震，規模5.7，花蓮震度4級以上，震央在花蓮近海，震源深度10公里，全台搖晃。<br />\n<br />\n7日晚間23點21分，花蓮再發生有感地震，規模5.7，花蓮震度4級以上，震央在花蓮近海，震源深度10公里，全台搖晃。地震時必須停止救援，影響救援行動。<br />\n<br />\n根據中央災害應變中心截至今（7）日21時統計，釀成6死、260人傷、67人失聯，有4處建築物倒塌或傾斜，包括統帥飯店、國盛六街2、4號；國盛六街41號；商校街2號的雲門翠堤大樓。其中最嚴重的雲翠大樓，目前仍有52人失聯，警消也連夜在低溫、大雨、餘震中搶救，希望把握救援的黃金時間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各地最大震度為：<br />\n<br />\n花蓮市、宜蘭南澳、南投合歡山：4級<br />\n<br />\n草嶺：3級<br />\n<br />\n台中、宜蘭、桃園、新竹、台北市信義區、苗栗、南投、新北市、嘉義、彰化、雲林、台東：2級<br />\n<br />\n基隆、高雄、台南、屏東、澎湖：1級"},{"pid":"aef59ac88b7d80153099c32888cc502252935fbb","tid":553624,"uid":21228,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"每晚震一震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頂到過年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a398ca37b39fd4f889633630ada5ffec4707c91","tid":553624,"uid":166663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:12:02.000Z","msg":"頭先餘震超大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5bfa3a6d2776adf3ef1ebb33f4f3e0f96b4a88","tid":553624,"uid":45929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:15:50.000Z","msg":"由星期日夜晚已經開始震....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c